Autumn Vixen

I dunno about you guys, but I love autumn. It brings about this feeling I don’t usually get with other parts of the year. The colors are pretty, the atmosphere is nice, and it also includes Halloween! Plus the aesthetic mixes well with one of my favorite animals, foxes.

I just imagine walking along the street with my vixen waifur, the autumn leaves drifting in the wind and piling up on the grass, and the gentle breeze hitting us. The temperature is cold, so we bundle up in warm clothes, but it’s not to the point of being uncomfortably freezing. I know this a far cry from what autumn usually is, especially considering where I live, but it’s the images that run through my mind this time of year.
